videos.description: Central Michigan's Larry Austin shows off his strength as he finishes through contact for an and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Austin muscles through contact for and-1

videos.description: Buffalo's Dontay Caruthers comes up with a steal and takes it all the way for a sick one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Caruthers steal leads to tomahawk slam

videos.description: Buffalo's Nick Perkins slips past Central Michigan's defenders and throws down a monster slam.
videos.headline: Perkins throws down 2-handed flush
